{
  "stem": "25809.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they paid money for a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how much they paid I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think it was double the normal rent, something to that effect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my, my father had, had money because of the business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had squirrelled money away, thrifty-like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And apparently, he had, he had money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So so far, so far that there would have come a point where he would be out of money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had to be, of course, very careful because he didn't know how long the war was going to last and if his money was going to last.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think the attitude was, as long as I have the money and the people are willing to accept the money and cover me, until nobody's willing to cover me and I don't have the money, then all I can do is, OK, I'll go to the Germans and give up.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or I show myself or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were kind of phlegmatic about it by saying, OK, we will stick it out as long as possible.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If we run out of money, OK, then I guess that's what's he'll, what we'll do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been a, a tremendous strain for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a kid, you don't realize that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been a tremendous amount of strain for him trying to figure out, how am I going to work all this?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How, how will I make it through these war years, buy food?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have a daughter, a son, and, and, and ourselves-- my father and mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How to do all this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, this, this tension and, and this fear was, was continuously there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is what made it, made it so, I, I think, horrifying for, for everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
